{"prompt": "Generate a website for a online magazine. The website should be artistic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artistic Blue Magazine</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0d47a1; /* Deep blue */\n            --secondary-color: #42a5f5; /* Lighter blue */\n            --text-color: #f5f5f5; /* Light gray for text */\n            --background-color: #1a237e; /* Very dark blue */\n            --accent-color: #808080; /* Dark gray for subtle accents */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n  